HEADWORD: Pillwort
<hw>Pill"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of the genus <gen>Pilularia</gen>; minute aquatic
cryptograms, with small pill-shaped fruit; -- sometimes called
<altname>peppergrass</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pilocarpine</ent>⟦br⟧
